mixin microModal(modalId)
    div.modal.micromodal-slide(id=modalId, aria-hidden="true")
        div.modal__overlay(tabindex="-1" data-micromodal-close)
            div.modal__container(role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby= modalId + "-title")
                header.modal__header
                    h2.modal__title(id=modalId + "-title") Bạn có chắc chắn muốn xóa không?
                    button.modal__close(aria-label="Close modal" data-micromodal-close)
                footer.modal__footer
                    button.modal__btn.modal__btn-primary(data-micromodal-close, type="button") Tiếp tục
                    button.modal__btn(data-micromodal-close, aria-label="Close this dialog window") Hủy bỏ

